<p><i><b>This Perfect Day</b></i> (<a href="/wiki/1970" title="1970">1970</a>), by <a href="/wiki/Ira_Levin" title="Ira Levin">Ira Levin</a>, is a <a href="/wiki/Heroic" title="Heroic" class="mw-redirect">heroic</a> <a href="/wiki/Science_fiction" title="Science fiction">science fiction</a> novel of a <a href="/wiki/Technocracy_(bureaucratic)" title="Technocracy (bureaucratic)">technocratic</a> <a href="/wiki/Utopia" title="Utopia">utopia</a>. It is often compared to <i><a href="/wiki/Nineteen_Eighty-Four" title="Nineteen Eighty-Four">Nineteen Eighty-Four</a></i> and <i><a href="/wiki/Brave_New_World" title="Brave New World">Brave New World</a></i>.</p>
